[div class=p 
	[em 
		"Avoid the Noid
	]em
	" is a platform computer game for the Commodore 64 and MS-DOS, written in 1989 to promote Domino's Pizza.
	$LF
	"It was modeled after the company's ad campaign during the late 1980s. The ads featured a "noid" that destroyed pizzas and must be avoided.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The protagonist must traverse a 30-story building and deliver the pizza within 30 minutes.
	$LF
	"Colorful rabbits armed with booby traps, phone bombs, rocket launchers and bomber planes that drop water balloons seek to prevent the delivery.
	$LF
]div
